        <body>
            <div1 xml:id="d001" type="work" decls="#md" met="E">
                <head>
                    <title>1</title>
                    <bibl source="digital">Barbara Zlobec</bibl>
                </head>
                <div2 xml:id="001c001" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>1</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l1" n="">1.</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l2" n="1">Pandite iam portas, miseri, et subducite pontes;</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l3" n="2">Nam Federicus adest, quem Gebelina sequor.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c002" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>2</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l4" n="tit.">2. Laurentius Collensis in ducem Calabriae Collem obsidentem</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l5" n="1">Dic, quid fulmineis evertis moenia bombis?</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l6" n="2">Pro muris stabunt pectora Colligenum.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c003" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>3</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l7" n="tit.">3. Hyeronimus Columna qui sub duce Calabriae | merebat in Collem obsessum</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l8" n="1">Diruta cesserunt bombis tua moenia: cedent</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l9" n="2">Diruta sic nostris pectora pectoribus.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c004" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>4</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l10" n="tit.">4. Laurentius Collensis in ducem Calabriae</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l11" n="1">Perfacile est putres tormentis rumpere muros,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l12" n="2">At fortes animos frangere difficile.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c005" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>5</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l13" n="tit.">5. Laurentius Collensis in ducem Calabriae</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l14" n="1">Dirue tecta, domos, villas et templa deorum:</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l15" n="2">Non deerit Tuscis nostra fides patribus.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c006" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>6</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l16" n="tit.">6. idem ad eundem</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l17" n="1">Quid laqueum, remos, praedas et vincla minaris?</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l18" n="2">Scit populus noster vincere sive mori.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c007" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>7</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l19" n="tit.">7. Laurentius Collensis ad ducem Calabriae Colle expugnato</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l20" n="1">Moenia nunc sileant gentes devicta Sagunti</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l21" n="2">Atque Syracusii bella cruenta soli;</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l22" n="3">Nulla Numantini memorentur fama triumphi</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l23" n="4">Et sileant fides moenia Massiliae:</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l24" n="5">Plus Collem vicisse fuit. De Colle loquantur:</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l25" n="6">Alphonso cessit Martia terra duci.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c008" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>8</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l26" n="tit.">8. idem ad Federicum Urbini ducem capto Colle</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l27" n="1">Quod fundis Tuscas gentes, quod Marte cruento</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l28" n="2">Pulsas munito moenia celsa loco,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l29" n="3">Haec est, o Federice, tuae quota portio famae:</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l30" n="4">Quod vincis Collem maxima summa fuit.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
            </div1>
